%section.full-width.our-story
  .container
    %h1 Thank You! Your Uruut Account is Now Active.
    - if current_user.coupon_stripe_token
      %h4= "You used a coupon: #{current_user.coupon_stripe_token}"

    %p{ style: 'margin: 12px 115px 35px;' }
      Set up your first campaign, access Uruut’s powerful donor relationship management tools, or just start exploring.

    - if user_signed_in? && current_user.campaign_manager?
      = link_to "/projects", method: :post do
        .btn
          Get started ►
    - else
      = link_to choose_plan_pages_path do
        .btn
          Get started ►


    %p{ style: 'margin: 50px 115px 10px;' }
      To help you get started, we will assign one of our campaign launch managers to <a href="http://meetme.so/UruutConsulting">schedule a kick-off call</a> with you to walk you through the campaign set up process and help answer any questions you might have.

    %p{ style: 'margin: 1px 115px 1px;' }
      <a href="http://meetme.so/UruutConsulting">Click here</a> to schedule your kick-off call.
